{"tid":2385371,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【遊戲驛站GME】Facebook將討論股票買賣群組羅賓漢下架","createTime":"2021-01-29T04:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T04:41:39.000Z","uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96d9bc4b6074fd15fe06febf4b44f98fabf8025d","tid":2385371,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"社交網站Facebook將討論股票買賣的群組羅賓漢（Robinhood Stock Traders）下架。這個群組有大約15.7萬人。<br />\n<br />\n該群組創建人指，周三收到Facebook通知要將群組下架，指群組違反FB政策，涉及成人性剝削（adult sexual exploitation），但透露沒有具體詳情。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲驛站GameStop（美：GME）上演「散戶屠鱷」，GME連日爆升後近一星期後尚未告終，導致沽空遊戲驛站的對沖投資機構要平倉止蝕離場。被視為引發散戶力量的網上討論區「r/WallStreetBets」成為市場關注，WallStreetBets在Reddit一度暫停開放，甚至被另一討論區Discord 下架。Disocrd指出，有關決定在WallStreetBets發現「仇視內容」，而非因為金融詐騙。"},{"pid":"ea702303d9d4c485770a4cdebff97f8aeddafe5e","tid":2385371,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"中共極權常見手段"},{"pid":"3d08a63c8e6b266be47cb7f612480209893891ed","tid":2385371,"uid":137647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"最後又係big tech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞完選舉再搞股票<br />\n睇下今次幾多美國人會醒"},{"pid":"4375b43731ab618e683e93f4ea0f4554318278bb","tid":2385371,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"美國人咩反應"},{"pid":"28fb86cb8cd845bb0df83bc912af450648d62c06","tid":2385371,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"Discord都用呢啲理由封撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfb0efb7bd2660012ddd40208557ad8577f3e77","tid":2385371,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4375b43731ab618e683e93f4ea0f4554318278bb","tid":2385371,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"美國人咩反應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"鵪鶉"}]}